<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>损害赔偿 on 曹义德律师专栏</title><link>https://caoyide.com/categories/%E6%8D%9F%E5%AE%B3%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</link><description>Recent content in 损害赔偿 on 曹义德律师专栏</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 03:20:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://caoyide.com/categories/%E6%8D%9F%E5%AE%B3%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>被人造谣说欠钱不还，朋友圈都传遍了——怎么恢复名誉？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%90%8D%E8%AA%89%E6%9D%83/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 03:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%90%8D%E8%AA%89%E6%9D%83/</guid><description>有人在朋友圈、微信群、小区公告栏散布你的不实信息。你的名誉受损了，法律怎么帮你恢复？</description></item><item><title>我的照片被商家拿去当广告了——能要多少钱？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9D%83/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E6%9D%83/</guid><description>你的照片被网店拿去当买家秀、被美容院拿去当案例、被培训机构拿去当学员见证——没经过你同意就是侵权。</description></item><item><title>在网上被人造谣了，怎么让对方删帖道歉赔钱？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 02:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B/</guid><description>有人在网上发帖造谣你、曝光你的隐私、煽动别人网暴你。删帖是第一诉求，但后续怎么走法律程序？</description></item><item><title>你的个人信息被卖了，能告谁？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2/</guid><description>刚买了房，装修公司电话就来了。刚生了孩子，早教机构就来推销。谁卖了你的信息？你能索赔多少？</description></item><item><title>你家狗咬了人，赔多少？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E5%92%AC%E4%BA%BA/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E5%92%AC%E4%BA%BA/</guid><description>遛狗没拴绳，咬了路人。医药费、误工费、精神损害抚慰金——狗主人要赔哪些？如果被咬的人先招惹了狗呢？</description></item><item><title>天上掉下来一个花盆，砸到人了——整栋楼都要赔？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%9B%E7%89%A9/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E9%AB%98%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%9B%E7%89%A9/</guid><description>高空抛物砸到人，找不到是谁扔的。整栋楼的住户都要赔吗？物业有责任吗？民法典说了什么？</description></item><item><title>网购的东西不想要了，商家说拆了包装不给退——合法吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E8%B4%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E8%B4%A7/</guid><description>网购的东西拆了包装还能退吗？哪些商品不适用七天无理由？商家拒退怎么办？</description></item><item><title>被人打了，除了报警还能做什么？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E4%BA%86/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E4%BA%86/</guid><description>被打了，很多人只知道报警。但报警只是第一步。如何验伤、如何索赔、是治安案件还是刑事案件——这些你都得知道。</description></item><item><title>买到了假货，除了退货还能让他赔你三倍</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</guid><description>买到假货别光退货。法律规定经营者欺诈的退一赔三，最低赔五百。很多人不知道这条，白白吃亏。</description></item></channel></rss>